## Typography

### Typefaces
- Headlines / Titles:   Sansation Bold (fallback: Georgia Bold, serif)
- Body / Labels:        Titillium Web Regular/Bold/Light (fallback: system-ui, sans-serif)
- Monospace (code):     ui-monospace, monospace

### Size Scale
- Cover / Hero title:   44–54pt / 2.75–3.375rem   Sansation Bold   White
- Page / Slide title:   32–40pt / 2–2.5rem         Sansation Bold   White
- Section header:       24–28pt / 1.5–1.75rem      Sansation Bold   White or Gamma Green
- Body copy:            14–16pt / 0.875–1rem        Titillium        White
- Badge / Pill label:   11–13pt / 0.69–0.81rem      Titillium Bold   White ALL CAPS
- Footer / Caption:     8–10pt  / 0.5–0.625rem      Titillium Light  Electric Blue
- Stat callout number:  60–72pt / 3.75–4.5rem       Sansation Bold   White or Electric Blue

### Typography Rules
- Titles: left-aligned on content views, centered on cover/hero views
- Body text: always left-aligned — never center paragraphs or bullet lists
- Letter-spacing on "ELEVATE" wordmark footer: ~0.3em wide tracking
- Never use Inter, Roboto, Arial, or system-default sans-serif for UI text

