## Component Patterns

### Backgrounds
- Primary page background: `#192036` (Elevate Navy)
- Never use white, off-white, or light grey as a primary background
- Atmospheric texture effects (aurora glow, wave lines) are on-brand for hero sections
- Aurora gradients: use blue-green spectrum — Electric Blue to Gamma Green

### Cards / Panels
- Background: `#1e2a45` or `rgba(255,255,255,0.04)` on navy
- Border: `1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)` or `1px solid #00aeef` for emphasis
- Border-radius: 8–12px for standard cards, 999px for pill badges
- Box-shadow: `0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)`

### Buttons
- Primary: Electric Blue `#00aeef` fill, white text, Titillium Bold, ALL CAPS, border-radius 6px
- Secondary: transparent fill, `1px solid #00aeef`, Electric Blue text
- CTA / signal: Gamma Green `#00fe7c` fill, navy `#192036` text (high contrast)
- Never use red or generic blue buttons

### Badges / Pills
- Background: Electric Blue `#00aeef` or Gamma Green `#00fe7c`
- Text: white (on Electric Blue) or navy `#192036` (on Gamma Green)
- Font: Titillium Bold, ALL CAPS, 11–13px
- Border-radius: 999px

### Data Visualization
Chart/graph series colors in order:
1. Electric Blue   `#00aeef`
2. Gamma Green     `#00fe7c`
3. Orbital Orange  `#ff9600`
4. Violet Vortex   `#723aca`
5. Solar Yellow    `#ffea37`
6. Binary Blue     `#0f75bd`

### Tables
- Header background: `#0f75bd` (Binary Blue) or `#192036` with `#00aeef` text
- Row background: alternating `#192036` / `#1e2a45`
- Border: `1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`
- Text: white; muted text at 60% opacity for secondary info

### Icons
- Stroke color: Electric Blue `#00aeef` or white
- Fill: Gamma Green `#00fe7c` for signal/CTA icons only
- Size: consistent 16px, 20px, or 24px — never mix sizes in the same row

